    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment panel reviewed all 13 credibility factors under ASME V&V 40-2018 at MRL 5. Seven factors were formally assessed; six remain as epistemic gaps. The supporting claim (https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-credibility) presents a comprehensive narrative of model credibility with Monte Carlo UQ results demonstrating 95th-percentile NIH below clinical threshold across all five VAD operating points. ValidationResults VR-2024-001 through VR-2024-005 provide detailed provenance chains to experimental and computational datasets. On balance, the panel accepted the package for regulatory submission with the understanding that epistemic gaps at MRL 5 are documented and will be addressed in a subsequent credibility update prior to final PMA submission.",
